{"TopicId":29014,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Is there a way to plant multiple Flags with just one kerbal?","CreatedByName":"Jaedinator","CreatedById":27680,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T09:15:27Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jaedinator","CreatedById":27680,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T09:15:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHey, I just landed on Ike as a flyby to Duna and planted a flag here, but then i saw that my kerbal pilot only got one flag. So when i fly to Duna, is there a way to place a flag there without taking the flag on Ike back?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThanks alot \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222013-05-25T09:20:15Z\u0022 title=\u002205/25/2013 09:20  AM\u0022 data-short=\u002211 yr\u0022\u003EMay 25, 2013\u003C/time\u003E by Jaedinator\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xandski","CreatedById":56858,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T09:18:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ve not tried it myself but does the flag get refreshed when you re-enter the lander? I\u0027d hope that Kerbals would keep spares for situations like this...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E... I might be wrong though.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jaedinator","CreatedById":27680,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T09:19:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EYou\u0027re right, thanks alot \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rodion_herrera","CreatedById":66284,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T10:04:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jaedinator\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Jaedinator\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESo when i fly to Duna, is there a way to place a flag there without taking the flag on Ike back?\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf Squad didn\u0027t allow flag respawns upon boarding your ship again, then that statement right there, is so \u003Cem\u003Eclassic\u003C/em\u003E Kerbal Space Station. I mean, the hilarity of having to go back to Ike and retrieve a flag, just so you can plant it on Dune...funny as hell. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xandski","CreatedById":56858,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T10:31:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027m more shocked that Kerbals have spares of something \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlexanderB","CreatedById":17544,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T11:40:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThey have spare fuses? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"drakesdoom","CreatedById":57297,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T13:55:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Eand toothbrushes.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tempes156","CreatedById":65696,"CreatedDateTime":"2013-05-25T19:22:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E...and tires, lots and lots of tires!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bjerrang","CreatedById":180617,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-20T18:18:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust land again. New flag is produced.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}